I’m so glad you’re here is out now! 10% of all proceeds will be donated to the American Foundation for Suicide Prevention ♡

This chapter means the most to us and we wanted to give back and support a cause that can help people when they don’t feel like they belong here.

We want people to see the message on these pieces and remember that they are not alone and someone is glad they’re with us.

Mental healthcare has always been of huge importance to us. We’ve all had people close to us who have struggled with this issue, who feel alone and need resources to help them through their battle and people to show them that they are not alone. 

The AFSP’s mission is to save lives and bring hope to those affected by suicide. They fund research to improve interventions, train clinicians in suicide prevention, and advocate for policy that will save lives. They work to find better ways to reach those who suffer, and encourage schools, workplaces, and communities to make mental health a priority.

Help us save lives this holiday season with every purchase. We’re so glad you’re here ♡
